          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἕρμα</span></b>  (1) (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">εἴρω</span> 2, root <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">σερ</span>): only pl., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἕρματα</span>,
